original_title: National Lampoon Live: New Faces: Vol. 1
overview: Hosted by Frank Caliendo (of Fox NFL Sunday and Mad TV), this collection showcases some of the funniest stand-up comedians from around the world. Famous for promoting the best comedians and bringing irreverent, side-splitting comedies such as Animal House and the Vacation series to the big screen, National Lampoon searched high and low to find the brightest, wackiest comedians around for this laugh-filled event.
title: National Lampoon Live: New Faces: Vol. 1
